featured_reviews.review_id:
Visited there for Quran Manadu. It was organized by this masjid executive committee. Really excited to watch the entire program they organized it well and the chief guest speeches were informative and the way conveyed is really enjoyable.

After very long time I spent a long night at this masjid. Especially the quirath recited by young people is really unforgettable, Masha Allah. I enjoyed their every flows of Quranic verses.

At last finally their hospitality, beautiful chicken biriyani with onion raitha, sweat, banana they served a hot and tasty food in a organized manner.

Kudos to all who contributed for the success of the event.

May Allah SWT bless you with good health, happy life and prosperity
